pg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-timberlake">贾斯汀·汀布莱克</a>已就醉酒驾驶 (DWI) 案件达成认罪协议，并将承认交通违规罪名。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/justin-timberlake-everything-i-thought-it-was-review-sullied-superstar-gets-trapped-in-the-typical-3601736">贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake) – 《我以为的一切》评论：被玷污的超级巨星陷入了典型的困境</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://www.tmz.com/2024/09/11/justin-timberlake-pleads-guilty-traffic-offense-not-dwi/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>TMZ 报道</i></a>，这位歌手的律师小爱德华·伯克 (Edward Burke Jr.) 和检察官让该案法官签署了这笔交易，因此酒后驾车指控现已被撤销。相反，汀布莱克将承认酒后驾驶 (DWAI) 罪名，这通常是比酒后驾车罪名更轻的罪名，是一种违法行为，而不是轻罪或重罪。</p><p> <i>TMZ</i>还报道称，汀布莱克将支付 300 至 500 美元的罚款。不过，法官将在周五（9 月 13 日）的听证会上确定具体​​金额，届时认罪协议将正式提交法庭。</p><p>这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nsync">*NSYNC</a>明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-arrested-for-driving-while-intoxicated-3766629">因涉嫌驾车冲过停车标志并偏离车道而于 6 月 18 日被捕</a>。他当时被指控犯有 SWI 轻罪。据称，他告诉警官他喝了一杯马提尼酒，正开着车跟着朋友回家。据信他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-timberlake-refused-breathalyser-when-arrested-for-driving-while-intoxicated-his-lawyer-says-3766720">拒绝接受呼气测试并在当地警察局过夜</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3792856" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3792856" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3792856" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/J-Timberlake-Mugshot.jpg" alt="贾斯汀·汀布莱克照片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/J-Timberlake-Mugshot.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/J-Timberlake-Mugshot-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/J-Timberlake-Mugshot-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/J-Timberlake-Mugshot-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/J-Timberlake-Mugshot-1392x884.jp